name: Bravo Fighter (V)
Lore: 'Flown by an unknown pilot who likes to spin a lot. Played the deciding role in the attack against the Droid Control Ship.',
Text: 'May add one astromech. During battle, may target a starship with no character piloting. Draw destiny. If destiny > defense value, target hit. Permanent pilot provides ability of 4. Immune to attrition < 3.',
